headline: How to Prepare for a ‘Lost Decade’ in Stocks
summary: Stocks have logged a historic run thanks to AI,  Nvidia  and other growth drivers, but some Wall Street strategists warn the market will spend the next decade feeling winded.  While the warnings are worth heeding, there are ways to protect yourself and possibly avoid a “lost decade” for stocks.  Steep valuations and extreme concentration in tech are the main causes for concern, according to Goldman Sachs.
